This project was developed as part of a Master in Data Management and
Curation internship conducted at the Laboratory of Data Engineering,
AREA Science Park.

The application was developed and validated in the Stencil virtual
datacenter: a virtualized multi-node environment with Kubernetes, Ceph
RADOS Gateway object storage, and identity/networking services used to
approximate production infrastructure during internship development.

